{
  "stem": "24111.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm very proud of having helped that way, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when after, I think, a few months in Amir-- by the way, I started to learn Hebrew-- Ivrit-- after a few months, perhaps a half a year, it was decided to go on our own.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were a group of perhaps 30 teenagers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We wanted to have our own kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we started under the name of Nahshonim in Ramat HaSharon, not far from Herzliya.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were given an small parcel of land on-- and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were given it free, but we had to pay back the money to the [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Kayemet. ?] And we started an agricultural settlement there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Later on, we built even an little factory extracting olive oil with-- with presses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the time came and it became apparent that, sooner or later, the climate in-- in-- in Palestine will change.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The British wanted to leave [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The United Nations debated if it should come to an partition, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the Arab [NON-ENGLISH], the Arab attacks on Jewish communities and on Jewish buses and the Jewish facilities, started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And, of course, the Jews reacted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And who reacted was the Palmah or the-- the Jews itself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "At that time, the Jewish community decided that the Negev was needed, whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And 16 places in the Negev were built, almost overnight, as strategic points.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was not really agricultural because we couldn't do anything at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And in most of those points there was no water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Water had to be trucked in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And Amir-- and Ramat HaSharon, Nahshonim, our kibbutz decided to occupy one point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "The point was named Chasli.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C-H-A-S-L-I, Chasli, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Alumim. ?] And 28 boys and girls, including me, went to the Negev.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Ramat Gan.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
